WEBVTT

00:07.879 --> 00:09.098
Kobe, you suck!

00:23.483 --> 00:28.679
I've been hating you...

00:31.235 --> 00:34.344
...too long...

00:35.387 --> 00:37.810
...to stop now.

00:40.911 --> 00:44.823
You're retiring.

00:47.921 --> 00:50.056
And you want to be free.

00:52.160 --> 00:55.239
My hate was growing stronger...

00:56.342 --> 01:00.485
...as you became a habit to me.

01:03.367 --> 01:04.297
Please,...

01:04.363 --> 01:06.503
...don't make me stop now.

01:07.817 --> 01:10.536
Well, I hate you with all my heart.

01:15.031 --> 01:16.229
I hate you.

01:16.471 --> 01:17.564
I hate you.

01:19.571 --> 01:23.545
Don't make me, don't make me.

01:24.267 --> 01:27.169
Don't make me stop now.

